title: Launcher issues
body: Any one having trouble getting LOL to start and launch? I tried uninstalling and reinstalling  but  that dint  work, any other  suggestions?

replies.body:
Hey there,

Could you try running through the [Connection Troubleshooting article](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues), let me know if anything there helps.
Same thing happened to me have you found anything out yet?
